---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="主页 | MySite">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <img src="/blog_pages/avatar.jpg" alt="Avatar" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full shadow-md3-2 mb-6 bg-white object-cover" transition:name="avatar" />
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-google-onSurface">你好，我是 <span class="text-google-blue text-2xl md:text-4xl">01110110 01101001 01100111 01101110 01111001</span></h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-google-onSurfaceVariant max-w-2xl mb-8">
      全栈键政/设计爱好者。白天把复杂问题简单化，晚上把简单问题键政化。欢迎来到我的数字地堡。
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/blog_pages/projects" class="bg-google-blue text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium shadow-md3-1 hover:shadow-md3-2 hover:bg-blue-600 transition-all active:scale-95">
        查看项目
      </a>
      <a href="/blog_pages/about" class="bg-white text-google-blue border border-google-surfaceContainer px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium shadow-sm hover:bg-google-surface transition-all active:scale-95">
        关于我
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 px-2">最新动态</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <Card href="/blog_pages/blog/hello-world">
        <div class="text-sm text-google-blue font-medium mb-2">2026-06-08</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Hello World: 我的全新博客</h3>
        <p class="text-google-onSurfaceVariant line-clamp-2">使用 Astro 和 Tailwind CSS 构建，采用 Google Material Design 3 设计规范，带来极致的阅读体验。</p>
      </Card>
      <Card href="/blog_pages/projects">
        <div class="text-sm text-google-green font-medium mb-2">项目更新</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">开源工具箱 v2.0 发布</h3>
        <p class="text-google-onSurfaceVariant line-clamp-2">全新的 UI 设计，增加了 JSON 格式化、正则表达式测试等实用功能。</p>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
